description: It’s A Dog’s World has its roots in the great cooking traditions of the South, where owner/chef, Bessie Johnson, first began creating delicious meals for her family and friends. Now, after years of operating neighborhood favorites in San Diego such as Magnolias Authentic Southern Dining and Bessie’s Garret, the Johnson family is letting the good times keep “rolling” with It’s A Dog’s World.Our menu features delicious hot dogs, sliders and more – with a twist. This isn’t your typical concession fare. Our food is inspired by international flavors and ingredients. We keep it interesting with new and changing menu items, as well as serving plenty of your favorites.So be on the lookout for our mobile kitchen in your neighborhood or work place. We look forward to seeing you!
name: It's A Dog's World
